<TITLE> Dy speaker backs all-party JS probe idea </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Mar 7 (bdnews24.com)  Deputy speaker Shawkat Ali backs the idea of an all-party parliamentary inquiry committee on the BDR bloodbath. "I believe it's a very legitimate demand, if all the parties agree, such a committee can be constituted," he said Saturday in response to demands by the main opposition BNP. "It isn't a bad idea. All parties will have representation in the committee if it is formed," he told reporters after emerging from a programme at the Jatiya Press Club. bdn
